QuestData.Title: Equipping Our Fleet
QuestData.Description: Commander, our fleet is going to require some custom naval equipment if we hope to stand a chance in this war. Find Salty Jorren down at the docks, he should be able to help us out.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: Find Salty Jorren on the docks.
QuestData.LogDescription: Meet Salty Jorren at the docks.
QuestData.RewardText: Equipment can really make a difference out there, let's see what I can do to help ya out.

Objectives.Objective: Find Salty Jorren on the docks
Find the Blast Furnace blueprints on the docks
